author: soureek
body:
#### PR description:

Updating TopMuEG skim for 2023 collisions with the latest trigger paths. The files DPGAnalysis/Skims/python/TopMuEGSkim_cff.py is updated with the latest paths.

#### PR validation:
PR is intended for CMSSW_13_0_X and the changes have tested with "/RelValTTbar_14TeV/CMSSW_13_0_0-130X_mcRun3_2022_realistic_v2-v1/GEN-SIM-RECO" dataset. No issue was observed.
title: Updating TopMuEG skim with latest trigger paths for 2023 collisions
